{"tid":1270492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七一爭票源 齊齊airdrop 登記做選民 踢走保皇黨","createTime":"2019-07-01T00:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:04:04.000Z","uid":161653,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67792e1d29f58af81f70debf03e6f132872d51c7","tid":1270492,"uid":161653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:09:01.000Z","msg":"今日好多人會出黎遊行 大家要襯機會呼籲多d人登記做選民 <br />\n<br />\n小弟前個post經巴打建議 可廣傳圖文叫人登記 <br />\n於是整左幅圖 <br />\n<br />\n經測試 airdrop一彈出黎就已經見到以下巴打個登記選民懶人包post標題 內附有關post既QR code:<br />\n［推上熱門］iphone可以2分鐘完成選民登記！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n至於有巴打問收到點掃QR code 唔多講了 用iphone show俾其他人掃又好 自己用app入gallary掃又好 唔詳細教了 相信大家都識用 唔洗下下要喂埋入口<br />\n<br />\n好好把握個機會<br />\n1. 遊行人多 可有效廣傳<br />\n2. 行行企企冇野做可以登記<br />\n3. 即share即做 好過平時網上呼籲完d人未必即刻做<br />\n跟住冇左件事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNbqBZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNbqBZg.png&h=bc32f22b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd1a2a4e154c2419f65d2a380ba4d3fa41344239","tid":1270492,"uid":161653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7acaf25bdbbb0c8605b66a3cef8e54a75862b0b1","tid":1270492,"uid":161653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"784ee532ca242f90e54b0d069aa8ca8e8e305aeb","tid":1270492,"uid":262313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efde1205ef50ed61df8c30a5410f9514466c13ae","tid":1270492,"uid":211645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f8cd0ea937cae9ccd0a8928df785092f5f0f126","tid":1270492,"uid":19215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"出街齊齊airdrop"},{"pid":"2c7fb5ca63f8fbcf75331badf9925e6f07818734","tid"